<TEXT>
GLASGOW-based W M Mann celebrated its 25th year in business with a 20%
leap in 1994 pre-tax profits to a record #823,000.
The family-controlled banking and property group said last year's
trading conditions had been less difficult than those encountered during
the previous two or three years.
