<DOCID>GH950323-000124</DOCID>
<DATE>950323</DATE>
<HEADLINE>Gunmen hunted</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>8</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>979255552</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
PARIS: Police launched a huge manhunt last night for three gunmen who
robbed a Paris bank and an armoured van, taking its driver and guard as
hostages, then shot dead a motorist who refused to let them steal his
car.
</TEXT>
