<TEXT>
A TEENAGER who went missing for four days has returned home. Tayside
Police confirmed that 15-year-old Sara Tanbini, of Brownhill Road,
Dundee, had come back to her family on Tuesday night. She had been
missing since going to a party with friends on Saturday.
</TEXT>
