<EDITION>1</EDITION>
<PAGE>4</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>979255563</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
SHOPLIFTER John Armstrong, 32, came away with less than he started
with. He dropped three pairs of trousers he had stolen -- and left his
