<DOCID>GH950323-000138</DOCID>
<DATE>950323</DATE>
<HEADLINE>Woman recovering</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>1</EDITION>
<PAGE>4</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>979255567</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
A WOMAN was recovering in Caithness General Hospital, Wick, yesterday
after being found after an intensive search. Miss Jane Dixon, 31, of
Whitelea Road, Kilmacolm, Renfrewshire, had slight head injuries and was
suffering from exposure after her car crashed.
</TEXT>
